<i>noun</i>: 소름 [소ː름] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소름 [소ː름]</dt><br>
<dd>goosebump</dd><br>
<dd>무섭거나 춥거나 징그러울 때 피부가 오므라들며 좁쌀 같은 것이 돋는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A millet-like thing that comes up on one's skin as it retracts when one is scared, cold or disgusted.</dd><br>
